title: Coconutty pumpkin bread
ingredients: ['400g caster sugar', '220g dark brown soft sugar', '250ml vegetable oil', '4 eggs', '425g pumpkin puree', '440g plain flour', '2 teaspoons bicarbonate of soda', '2 teaspoons salt', '1/2 teaspoon ground cloves', '1 1/2 teaspoons ground cinnamon', '1 teaspoon ground allspice', '1 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '150ml water', '75g desiccated coconut', '60g chopped walnuts']
